5000|$|The old San Giorgio {{society which}} had been renamed Santa Anastasia after {{the first world war}} now {{incorporated}} other teams and changed the name to Scuola Campanaria Verona in S.Anastasia (Bellringing school of Verona based in S.Anastasia church). In the Veneto region there are about 2,500 <b>bell</b> <b>ringers</b> of the Veronese method, united in local teams, more than half of which are members of the [...] "Associazone Suonatori di Campane a Systema Veronese" [...] (ASCSV) or association of <b>bell</b> <b>ringers</b> of the Veronese method.|$|R
